#: ../../src/reference/security/data-protection.rst:76
msgid ""
"**Measures for admission control ensure that unauthorized persons cannot "
"physically access the data processing equipment.**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../src/reference/security/data-protection.rst:79
msgid ""
"The physical assets (servers, switches, hard drives, ...) are located in "
"EU data centers operated by third parties. The ownership of the physical "
"equipment is with the Flying Circus, or, in special cases by our "
"customers [#customer-owned]_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../src/reference/security/data-protection.rst:84
